data.description:
Please allow me to introduce you to this 3 bedroom (with potential to be 4) home located in Orchard View school district! 
 
With 2 large living rooms, a 3 season porch, AND a 30x30 garage you will have an ton of room for activities!

The bathroom and two bedrooms are on the main level, an extra large finished space for a third bedroom is upstairs.
There is also a partially finished (could be 4th bedroom) with a huge walk in closet that just needs an egress window to finish it off, in the basement.

The basement of this home has one of the best condition cinderblock foundations I have ever seen. 
There is an on-demand water heater & this home has a large lot with a fenced in space behind the home.
